S:@T1[33]=[code:i,message:s,category:s,description:s]
D:defaults=category=Client Error
D:category=Informational,Success,Redirection,Client Error,Server Error
@T1:
F:csv
!,100,Continue,The server has received the request headers and the client should proceed to send the request body.,Informational
2t,Switching Protocols,The requester has asked the server to switch protocols.,0
5k,OK,The request was successful.,1
5l,Created,The request was successful and a resource was created.,1
5m,Accepted,The request has been accepted for processing\, but not completed.,1
5o,No Content,The request was successful but there is no content to send.,1
5q,Partial Content,The server is delivering only part of the resource due to a range header.,1
8d,Moved Permanently,The resource has been permanently moved to a new URL.,2
8e,Found,The resource resides temporarily at a different URL.,2
8f,See Other,The response can be found at a different URL using GET.,2
8g,Not Modified,The resource has not been modified since last requested.,2
8j,Temporary Redirect,The resource temporarily resides at a different URL.,2
8k,Permanent Redirect,The resource has been permanently moved\, use same method.,2
b4,Bad Request,The server cannot process the request due to client error.
b5,Unauthorized,Authentication is required and has failed or not been provided.
b7,Forbidden,The server understood the request but refuses to authorize it.
b8,Not Found,The requested resource could not be found.
b9,Method Not Allowed,The request method is not supported for the resource.
ba,Not Acceptable,The resource is not available in a format acceptable to the client.
bc,Request Timeout,The server timed out waiting for the request.
bd,Conflict,The request conflicts with the current state of the server.
be,Gone,The resource is no longer available and will not be available again.
bh,Payload Too Large,The request is larger than the server is willing to process.
bi,URI Too Long,The URI provided was too long for the server to process.
bj,Unsupported Media Type,The media format of the request is not supported.
bm,I'm a Teapot,The server refuses to brew coffee because it is a teapot.
bq,Unprocessable Entity,The request was well-formed but semantically incorrect.
bx,Too Many Requests,The user has sent too many requests in a given time.
dw,Internal Server Error,The server encountered an unexpected condition.,4
dx,Not Implemented,The server does not support the functionality required.,4
dy,Bad Gateway,The server received an invalid response from an upstream server.,4
dz,Service Unavailable,The server is not ready to handle the request.,4
e0,Gateway Timeout,The server did not receive a timely response from an upstream server.,4
END:@T1